cello.alt.servlet.scripting
Class DirectoryScriptLoader

java.lang.Object
  cello.alt.servlet.scripting.ScriptLoader
      cello.alt.servlet.scripting.DirectoryScriptLoader

public class DirectoryScriptLoader
extends ScriptLoader

This class provides a standard filesystem directory based ScriptLoader. That is, it looks for .js files in its path and returns new FileScript objects.

Author:
Marcello
